divs: Sighting Details we were in the backyard and looked to the east and noticed a strip of white gold light just suspended in the sky...we couldn't tell the distance and it lasted only a few seconds..then I saw a line below of light..then it was gone...no movement.....the light was very well defined....we felt like we had seen something unnatural....still in awe
Summary: Strip of white light, bar like, with a thin line of light below, seemed suspended.
